<h2 id="2021-leadership-team">2021 leadership team</h2>

<p>Brigade membership is open to all, regardless of expertise or skill level. The brigade is led by core team of elected leads. Activities and formal decision-making are overseen by a Steering Committee, which meets monthly and consists of the elected leads plus project representatives.</p>

